# Go lang backend example tracking events from blockchain

This example track events from given contract 

### Installation

1. Install go lang (see [instruction](https://go.dev/doc/install))
2. Clone repository
```bash
$ git clone git@github.com:mirage-xyz/mirage-serverside-demo.git
$ cd backends/event-tracking-go
```
3. Install dependencies
```bash
$ go build
```
4. Deploy server
```bash
$ go run main.go
```

Pay attention that go lang need [GCC](https://gcc.gnu.org/install/) for work.